      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to take a look! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me through every commute and weekend trip. It's got plenty of life left and is just waiting for a new home. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
