    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It's got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking great and running smoothly. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
