    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders with the critical double VANOS system recently overhauled for precision timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential that maintains exceptional lockup. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and refreshed trailing arm bushings to ensure structural rigidity during high-lateral load cornering. While the aesthetics show a light, honest patina consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system components and rod bearing clearances\u2014are within tight tolerances. A true driver\u2019s specification for those who prioritize tactile feedback and engineering integrity.",
